title: Google\Cloud\Talent\V4beta1\ListJobsRequest
name: ListJobsRequest
description:
Input only.

List jobs request.

Generated from protobuf message google.cloud.talent.v4beta1.ListJobsRequest

Extends Google\Protobuf\Internal\Message

params.name: data
params.description: Optional. Data for populating the Message object.

params.name: data.parent
params.description: Required. The resource name of the project under which the job is created. The format is "projects/{project_id}", for example, "projects/api-test-project".

params.name: data.filter
params.description: Required. The filter string specifies the jobs to be enumerated. Supported operator: =, AND The fields eligible for filtering are: companyName (Required) requisitionId (Optional) Sample Query: companyName = "projects/api-test-project/companies/123" companyName = "projects/api-test-project/companies/123" AND requisitionId = "req-1"

params.name: data.page_token
params.description: Optional. The starting point of a query result.

params.name: data.page_size
params.description: Optional. The maximum number of jobs to be returned per page of results. If [job_view][google.cloud.talent.v4beta1.ListJobsRequest.job_view] is set to [JobView.JOB_VIEW_ID_ONLY][google.cloud.talent.v4beta1.JobView.JOB_VIEW_ID_ONLY], the maximum allowed page size is 1000. Otherwise, the maximum allowed page size is 100. Default is 100 if empty or a number < 1 is specified.

params.name: data.job_view
params.description: Optional. The desired job attributes returned for jobs in the search response. Defaults to [JobView.JOB_VIEW_FULL][google.cloud.talent.v4beta1.JobView.JOB_VIEW_FULL] if no value is specified.
